Q. What do you know of it? - A. I saw the prisoner Thompson come out of the Turk's Head;
James Attkins
came out after him.

- SOLOMONS sworn. - I redeemed these things; I live facing the Play-house, in Wooburn-street;
Mary Kelly
and the prisoner left the duplicates; I redeemed the coat and the telescope, and I gave 32s. for them (produces them); I had the duplicates from the prisoner; on the 12th of October the officer and the prosecutor came to me, and I shewed them the property; the coat was all over powder and dirt, and I had it scowered. - (The coat was identified by Mr. Brown.)
